title: Mazraeh-ye Shahid Hoseynzadeh
text: Mazraeh-ye Shahid Hoseynzadeh (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Mazra‘eh-ye Shahīd Ḩoseynzādeh) is a village in <a href="Khursand%20Rural%20District">Khursand Rural District</a>, in the <a href="Central%20District%20%28Shahr-e%20Babak%20County%29">Central District</a> of <a href="Shahr-e%20Babak%20County">Shahr-e Babak County</a>, <a href="Kerman%20Province">Kerman Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 94, in 23 families.
